MMR / Smmr
----------
The MMR decoder implements CCITT Group 4. Its run-length code tables
(src/mmr_tables.js) are the public ITU-T T.6 / T.4 standard codes.

IW44 wavelet
------------
The IW44 quantization steps and band structure follow the published IW44
wavelet design (L. Bottou et al.) and match DjvuNet's.

DjVuLibre
---------
DjVuLibre (GPL) was used ONLY as a conformance test oracle during development —
i.e. to encode the sample .djvu files used to validate decoder output. No
DjVuLibre source code is included in, derived into, or distributed with this
project.
